            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Imperante domno nostro 
                            Lodohvvico magno <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs> anno imperi sui undecimo, die tercio
                        de mense iunio indicione nona. Per anc pagina livellis do adque trado ego
                            <persName key="#Abbots #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            ref="#people/1237">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries">monesterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots #Coloni/tenants #Monasteries #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Coloni/tenants #Gai #Petiae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Fruits/vegetables #Operae #Minores #Legumes #Maiores #Rent_in_kind"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47"><placeName key="#Monasteries"
                                ref="#places/15">Nonantolas</placeName></orgName> tibi vero
                        <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #Freeborn"><name ref="Ursus">Ursoni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">libero hominem</rs>, idest <rs key="#Petiae">pecia</rs>
                        una de tera ..3.. aradoria qui est positas in <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Coloni/tenants #Gai #Petiae #Canals #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Fruits/vegetables #Operae #Minores #Legumes #Maiores #Rent_in_kind" ref="#places/2492">Ostilia</placeName>, qui
                        pertenit da parte ipsius monesterio, in tantum in quantum ante os dies per
                                <persName><name ref="Aribertus">Arreperto</name></persName> rectam
                        fuit, ipsa peciola tinente uno caput in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio Pado</rs>,
                        alio caput in <rs key="#Gai">gagio</rs>, de alio latus <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Domenico</name></persName>, de alio latus <rs
                            key="#Canals">Luvolam</rs>, ipsa peciola do tibi vel ad tuis heredis, et
                        ego <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">colonus</rs> vel meis heredis ibidem super
                        resedere repromito, lavorare et meliorare debeat sine fraude vel nelicto,
                           livellario nomine, usque ad annis
                        nomero viginti et nove. Et <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">reditum exinde
                            persolvere</rs> repromito ego colonus vel meis heredis ad parte ipsius
                        monesterio aut ad eius miso quid supervenerit de omnium laborem quem ibidem
                        Dominus laborantibus dederit: de <rs key="#Maiores">maiorimen</rs> cova
                        quarta in campo, <rs key="#Legumes">legumen</rs> modio quarto in area, <rs
                            key="#Minores">menudo</rs> modio quinto in area, lino magna quarta. <rs
                            key="#Exenia">Esenio</rs> vero per omni anno dinarios quatuor et ipso
                        esenio datum et conpletum sit in misa Sancti Martini. <rs key="#Operae"
                            >Operas</rs> vero per omni anno manibiles die sex et ipsas operas facere
                        debeat in Ostilia cum annona domnica; per tempore mesis vel vindimias <rs
                            key="#Actionarii/actores">miso domnico</rs> cum onore sussipiendum et
                        sucepta faciendum repromito; sic tamen ipso censum vel reditum colonus vel
                        eius heredis cum suo dispendio vegere debeat ad <rs key="#Cells/hermitages"
                            >cellam</rs> nostra in <placeName key=" #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Minores #Legumes #Maiores #Rent_in_kind #Cells/hermitages" ref="#places/1538"><geogName key="#Cells/hermitages #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Minores #Legumes #Maiores #Rent_in_kind"
                                ref="#estates/1111">Piscaria</geogName></placeName> et consignare
                        repromito ad miso domnico nam alio nullam. Ego patrono vel mei sucepsores te
                        suprascripto colonus nec ad tuis heredis nullam superinponere debeamus nisi
                        qualiter superiuscriptum est. Pena vero inter nobis stetit qui non
                        conpleverit vel permanserit in eo homnia qualiter superius legitur, et certe
                        aparuerit veritas, tunc conponat pars partis ubi culpa respeserit ad ilia
                        parte qui in sua fidem permanserit pena nomine solidos viginti et nove, pos
                        pena soluta pagina in sua maneat firmitatem. Duos livellos uno tinore
                        scriptis ad omnia suprascripta. Acto Ostilia, feliciter. Et de <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto</rs> et de rapas et fasiolis unde non
                        redatis. Signum (S) manus. Signum (S) manus. Signum (S) manus.</ab>
